# KuralVaasi 🎧

**KuralVaasi** is a Python-based application that brings the timeless wisdom of the Thirukkural to life. 
Users can search for verses and listen to them in Tamil, making it an engaging tool for learners and enthusiasts.

## 📦 Features
- 🔍 Search Thirukkural by number or keyword
- 🔊 Audio playback for each verse
- 🗂️ Includes Tamil and English text files
- 🧰 Simple Python scripts for easy use

## 🚀 Getting Started

Clone the repo and run the main script:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/jesman/kuralVaasi.git
cd kuralVaasi
python main.py
